   exclusively with B.H.

4. No contributor may claim authorship or co-ownership of PantheonOS,
   its kernels, its daemon suite, or its doctrine.

5. You agree not to submit contributions with restrictive licenses.

This Agreement protects the continuity, authorship,
and integrity of the PantheonOS project.